transcripts: The watch case with drawer holds up to six watches that have watch forms to help watch bands keep their shape. There is a glass window lid to display watches and keep them clean and protect it. The lower drawer has multiple compartments to hold keys, cuff-lings, money clips, or keepsakes. The watch winder holds up to two watches, electrically powered it comes with an ac adapter and automatically wined kinetic watches. It has three different rotation modes and a glass window lid to keep watches clean and protected. The Hudson watch case and watch winder by Kenneth Cole reaction home are available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores. Make sure to view the other items available in the men's Hudson collection.
